      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model justified for sub-yield loading regime; elasto-plastic model employed for post-yield regime with isotropic hardening calibrated to titanium alloy coupon data. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) between screw and vertebral body block justified by literature. Sensitivity analysis confirmed model form choices account for >95% of QoI variance."
