    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is accepted on the basis of conservative acceptance bounds, high sample count (N=11), and consistency across two independent laboratories. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; signature workflow is pending and will be completed prior to regulatory submission.",
